Final generated output to be used to generate workplan for Finance

sourceValue.sqlQuery: SELECT title, parenttask, projectteam, workplantasktype FROM Workplan WHERE 1=1 AND (projectteam = 'Accounting and Finance' OR projectteam = 'Finance') AND (_TransactionType LIKE '%Transformation%' OR _TransactionType IS NULL) AND (_Sector LIKE '%Government and Public Sector%' OR _Sector IS NULL) AND (_Industry LIKE '%Government and Public Sector%' OR _Industry IS NULL)
